
For deploying the var REFS app into a REFS environment:

* Shutdown the local REFS environment if it is already running.

* Setup sample app in the var folder. 
    servicesApp folder can be copied from LESDIR/samples/web/refs into the var folder as a starting point for your custom app.

* From a command line where environment is bootstrapped, change directory into the servicesApp folder.

* Run ant to deploy the app to the REFS folder (REFSDIR must be set).

* Run REFS database migration to load the custom app data

* Start the REFS environment.